               <div class="t m0 x12 h3 y78 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws1">IMPORT<span class="_ _2"></span>ANT<span class="_ _2"></span>:<span class="ff3 ws2"> Please read the guidance notes on the pr<span class="_ _0"></span>evious page before filling in this form <span class="ws1"> </span></span></div>
               <div class="t m0 x12 h3 y79 ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws2">and write clearly in <span class="ff4">black ink</span> using CAPIT<span class="_ _2"></span>AL LETTERS<span class="ff4 ws1">.</span></div>
