            </span></div>
               <div class="t m0 xf h3 y7c ff3 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws2">If yes, please give the company name below: <br><span style="top: 80%; font-family: sans-serif;line-height: 0;">{!! nl2br(e(wordwrap(\Illuminate\Support\Str::limit($driverConsentForm->making_an_enquiry_details, 80, ''), 43, "\n", true))) !!}</span> </div>
